Report Iraceplot

Source: R/report.R
report.Rd

Report Iraceplot

report(format = "html", irace_results = NULL, irace_file = NULL, file_name)

Arguments

format

String, either "pdf" or "html". The parameter according to its value is how the output file format will be. By default it is "html"
irace_results

The data generated when loading the Rdata file created by irace
irace_file

String, indicate the location where the Rdata file is located (example: "~/path-to/file.Rdata")
file_name

String, file name indicating where to save a pdf file with the plot. A pdf extension will be added to the file name provided (example: "~/path-to/file_name")

Value

document

Examples

NULL

#> NULL
